MIGRATION RULES

Never:
- Edit old migrations in a real project
- Duplicate:
  - Columns
  - Indexes
  - Foreign keys

Remember:
- morphs() creates:
  - subject_type
  - subject_id
  - index
- unique() creates index
- foreignId()->constrained() creates index

If schema is wrong:
- Create a NEW migration

If unsure:
- STOP and ask before changing
